Program: Jpaint
Author: Joel Moore
License: GPLv3
Version: 1.3

Desciption

Jpaint is a simple paint program written in python with pygame.

Controls

Draw: left mouse button
Erase: right mouse button
Save image: s *
Load image: l **
Left arrow: color red
Up arrow: color green
Right arrow: color blue
Down arrow: color black
Credits: c

* As of this version images will be saved in the same directory as Jpaint

** As of this version images will be loaded from the same directory as Jpaint
